      "message": "fix(rpc): Clarify wrong-network address errors\n\nDetect when an otherwise valid address belongs to a different network\\nand surface a specific error for generatetoaddress, generateblock, and\\nwalletcreatefundedpsbt change addresses. Keep the existing generic\\nmessages for malformed inputs.\\n\\nAdd functional coverage for uniquely identifiable and ambiguous wrong-\\nnetwork addresses so the new RPC behavior stays locked in.\\n\\nFixes #26290",
